{"tid":2124825,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國土安全部成立應對中國威脅特別小組","createTime":"2020-07-25T16:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T17:55:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b8c7ba091d6cdb448d7cd652ab4c94f4176d61","tid":2124825,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539882-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539882-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHSQscPELFEQk1IFn5y5IyWs%3D&h=0aa5bcaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539882-20200725.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2cced924\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539882-20200725.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中美關係持續緊張，美國國土安全部宣布成立特別小組，應對來自中國的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n代理部長沃爾夫說，中共在貿易、網絡安全、移民及知識產權領域的惡意活動，對美國的威脅正以驚人速度加劇。新成立的小組，將會優先處理、協調及闡明中國對美國構成的即時與長期威脅，強調會致力保障美國經濟、國家安全與自由，免受中共有系統地破壞。<br />\n<br />\n沃爾夫又說，國土安全部會繼續應對中國的網絡攻擊、經濟間諜活動及虛假信息宣傳活動。"},{"pid":"f755e3e7dd8a06e0d781007b381eeb4fd1fa1798","tid":2124825,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDF9twyq.gif&amp;h=96055489&amp;s=540\" /> 加速"},{"pid":"afba108e96e35e4cd68bb604c196c4bb781f5f3f","tid":2124825,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"習近平：我都要成立中共中央反美帝國主義領導小組，然後自己做組長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/project/20170925-china/img/pastContent/shi_title.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fproject%2F20170925-china%2Fimg%2FpastContent%2Fshi_title.jpg&h=af6a68d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"266bf2b2c6aa8